      • confidence

        @Deprecated
public float confidence
        Deprecated. 
        Hand detection confidence (0.0 = 0%, 100.0 = 100%). This is a the confidence level of the detected handedness. This is based on which hand model is more prominent in the detection algorithm. The value is in the range [0,100]. 0 is low confidence and 100 is high confidence on the handedness (left/right).
